The package boost-stacktrace is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS stacktrace)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::stacktrace)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_stacktrace REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::stacktrace)
